$\Rightarrow$ $\hat\alpha=\Sexpr{round(r.bodyfat$coef[1],2)}$ ,  $\hat\beta=\Sexpr{round(r.bodyfat$coef[2],2)}$, $\hat\sigma_e = \Sexpr{round(summary(r.bodyfat)$sigma,2)}$.
}


